# 📅 Day 4 – Aggregate Functions

## Topics Covered

- COUNT()
- SUM()
- AVG()
- MIN()
- MAX()

## Brief Explanation

Aggregate functions perform calculations on multiple rows.

### Examples

Count

```sql
SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM Employees;
```

Average

```sql
SELECT AVG(salary)
FROM Employees;
```

Maximum

```sql
SELECT MAX(salary)
FROM Employees;
```

Minimum

```sql
SELECT MIN(salary)
FROM Employees;
```

Sum

```sql
SELECT SUM(salary)
FROM Employees;
```

